- Afdeling 5: Can I offer this practice to my employees? What will it do for
my organization?
-

Organizations will notice more stress resilience and less burnout in their
organization. People being more capable to cope with challenges and
pressure. Consequently less sick-leave.
Also, people will come up more with creative ideas, as well as better
conduct: adherence to corporate policies. Better company atmosphere.
More openness, willingness to cooperate with colleagues. Employees will
turn out to be more valuable to your organization and contribute more
to its objectives.
